OL,3,CNumber of asylum seekers in hotels up
OL,4,C8% in first year of Labour government
OL,6,FThe number of asylum seekers living in
OL,7,FUK hotels has risen by 8% under Labour
OL,8,Fcompared to the same point last year,
OL,9,Fdespite falling slightly since March
OL,10,Fthis year.
OL,12,FThe figures come after the
OL,13,Fgovernment's plans to reduce the
OL,14,Fasylum backlog have been frustrated in
OL,15,Frecent days by a High Court issued an
OL,16,Finterim injunction barring the housing
OL,17,Fof migrants at a hotel in Essex.
