OL,3,CNumber of asylum seekers in hotels up
OL,4,C8% in first year of Labour government
OL,6,FThe judgement has led to many other
OL,7,Fcouncils considering their own legal
OL,8,Faction over asylum hotels - ITV News
OL,9,Funderstands 24 local authorities are
OL,10,Flooking into potential legal
OL,11,Fchallenges.
OL,13,FThe latest Home Office data, published
OL,14,Fon Thursday as part of the usual
OL,15,Fquarterly immigration statistics,
OL,16,Fcovers Labour's first year in office.
OL,18,FThey show there were 32,059 asylum
OL,19,Fseekers in UK hotels by the end of
OL,20,FJune.
