OL,3,CNumber of asylum seekers in hotels up
OL,4,C8% in first year of Labour government
OL,6,FThis was up from 29,585 at the same
OL,7,Fpoint a year earlier, when the
OL,8,FConservatives were still in power, but
OL,9,Fdown slightly on the 32,345 figure at
OL,10,Fthe end of March.
OL,12,FThe government has promised to end the
OL,13,Fuse of hotels to house asylum seekers
OL,14,Fby the end of this parliament.
OL,16,FThe latest number is still below the
OL,17,Fpeak of 56,042 asylum seekers in
OL,18,Fhotels at the end of September 2023
OL,19,Funder the Tories.
