OL,3,CNumber of asylum seekers in hotels up
OL,4,C8% in first year of Labour government
OL,6,FThe statistics also showed the average
OL,7,Fnumber of people on each small boat
OL,8,Fhas increased every year to 56 people
OL,9,Fper boat in the year ending June 2025
OL,10,Fcompared with 51 people per boat in
OL,11,Fthe year ending June 2024.
OL,13,FThe month of June 2025 saw the highest
OL,14,Fmonthly average on record, with 65
OL,15,Fpeople per boat.
OL,17,FA total of 43,000 people came to the
OL,18,FUK by small boat in the last year, an
OL,19,Fincrease of 38% on the previous year,
OL,20,Fbut slightly lower than the peak in
OL,21,Farrivals at 46,000 in 2022.
