OL,3,CNumber of asylum seekers in hotels up
OL,4,C8% in first year of Labour government
OL,6,FThe statistics on the number of asylum
OL,7,Fseekers arriving via small boats and
OL,8,Fstaying in hotels will be unwelcome
OL,9,Fnews for the government after the
OL,10,Fmajor High Court ruling on the Bell
OL,11,FHotel in Essex this week.
OL,13,FThe request to issue the injunction
OL,14,Fwas made by Epping's Conservative-led
OL,15,Fcouncil and has sparked a chain
OL,16,Freaction of other authorities across
OL,17,Fthe whole political spectrum,
OL,18,Fsignalling they will pursue similar
OL,19,Fcourses of action.
