OL,3,CNumber of asylum seekers in hotels up
OL,4,C8% in first year of Labour government
OL,6,FThese include Labour-run Tamworth and
OL,7,FWirral councils, Tory-run Broxbourne
OL,8,Fand East Lindsey councils and Reform's
OL,9,FStaffordshire and West
OL,10,FNorthamptonshire councils.
OL,12,FITV News' Paul Brand said that sources
OL,13,Fwithin the party feel that councils
OL,14,Fare going to waste taxpayers' money
OL,15,Ffighting a government that is already
OL,16,Fworking to end the use of hotels by
OL,17,Fasylum seekers.
